In fact, she dutifully obliged by enrolling in nursing school. Ultimately, she decided to explore her own creative path.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rFeloLT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JYY4d4v.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>While on vacation one day, Ms. Ade was frustrated by the lack of diversity in the design of the swimsuits. None of the options spoke to the Afrocentric exceptionalism she desired to present. 

